{"tid":2096474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"為何10年來Apink從未傳出戀愛消息？","createTime":"2020-07-06T06:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T02:54:20.000Z","uid":1086,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0c80d9b9bc750dcdf12859d69ad405b22af810bd","tid":2096474,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/25/180708_Sangam_Fan_Signing_Apink.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F2%2F25%2F180708_Sangam_Fan_Signing_Apink.jpg&h=70de8fae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n身為Idol女團Apink隊長初瓏，對於藝人的公開戀愛與否有著自己的一套見解。最近初瓏演出電影《不良的家族》，日前接受訪問也特別提到了這點。<br />\n<br />\n初瓏說：「周圍的人比我更常提到年齡問題，當我25歲的時候周圍的人都覺得嚇一跳而且有點受傷，現在比較不會，年齡一年比一年增長是很自然的事情，而且Apink成員們本來就都很年輕，我就好好躲在裡面就好。」相當搞笑的初瓏隊長，大家千萬不要討論她的年紀喔XD。不過初瓏說體力卻隨著年齡增加不減反增，更是時常運動讓自己成為團體內最活蹦亂跳的一位。<br />\n<br />\n初瓏坦言以前不懂釋放壓力，只會用哭的。「某一次開始跟成員們傾訴了真心話，原本覺得把自己的苦衷告訴她們會很對不起她們，但成員們也都開始相互傾訴煩惱或認真討論的時候，我也就開始這樣了，也開始學會了表達的方法，不會再想着要自己吞下去。」<br />\n<br />\n過去10年之間Apink從未傳出戀愛緋聞，也沒有公開戀情。初瓏說：「只有老么曾說：「姊姊，即使談戀愛也不要被逮到。」甚至有吻戲也要很小心注意。」對於是否覺得應該公開戀愛？初瓏說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">個人的想法是覺得，安靜低調的交往然後直接發表結婚這樣不好嗎？不管是交往時很開心還是分手了很傷心都好。其實這似乎是對粉絲們的一種必要的禮貌。</span>」"},{"pid":"d3800241bbfa1a358266d9d939e451f5bfc2e50a","tid":2096474,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"姐係老太婆就嚟結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bc69c4f3f57267db865fce72eb4cb0a947bc37","tid":2096474,"uid":44318,"like":3,"dislike":17,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"全部老虔婆 梗係冇啦"},{"pid":"1bf7822e159c387c19cfba5835e3b48e7cf93579","tid":2096474,"uid":189235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:08:53.000Z","msg":"好似金鍾大咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96ba4d94bf16114a6551fd90ad9e8e8e49ceb66","tid":2096474,"uid":294121,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:10:10.000Z","msg":"30歲仲賣清純<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵鬼信咩<br />\nKpop圈咁能亂<br />\n叫樸初瓏😍解下畫"},{"pid":"3d6a10c5db51928b79a67fd18206c7be600d8750","tid":2096474,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:16:07.000Z","msg":"仲有邊個係處？"},{"pid":"445f2310bb293549ecb0d070f01d00b8b532ed1b","tid":2096474,"uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b96ba4d94bf16114a6551fd90ad9e8e8e49ceb66","tid":2096474,"uid":294121,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:10:10.000Z","msg":"30歲仲賣清純<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />搵鬼信咩<br />\nKpop圈咁能亂<br />\n叫樸初瓏😍解下畫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:18:52.000Z","msg":"冇清純好耐啦ching..."},{"pid":"655a8f802b1dc51deb893dcd26992c485d9682fe","tid":2096474,"uid":14027,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"以前初瓏講過男神係rain<br />\n都希望佢搵個man嘅另一半<br />\n唔好同啲死臭飛一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57c1b2638c702226a268f9d399b5a86053abdf3b","tid":2096474,"uid":183332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"有兵驚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b683954480c3dcb894229116bcba798c35fd021d","tid":2096474,"uid":232077,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"小瓏女講得好岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拍拖唔係問題，唔好俾人知就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n縱觀成個K-pop界，由公開拍拖去到收成正果結婚幾乎冇<br />\n就算結左婚果啲都係奉子成婚收埋山冇再出黎撈<br />\n<br />\n仲想撈娛樂圈既根本就唔會公開拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n公開果啲十有九都係想抄作新聞，上下頭條<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以話Apink係K-pop清泉完全冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cd9416a814b3df2b4f520cdb2d87a9f81e69e7","tid":2096474,"uid":8795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"爆料區咪有囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e218367b1ac3b6a5b8ca4a5f07205f572a6848","tid":2096474,"uid":2781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:33:18.000Z","msg":"呢個真係apink最神奇嘅地方嚟"},{"pid":"25741a7fa0d54398652988299bf2cc287411d2a7","tid":2096474,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:37:48.000Z","msg":"佢地幾正 想屌"},{"pid":"4fb0df76587a28f604556848f84ebd328937d510","tid":2096474,"uid":294121,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e6cd9416a814b3df2b4f520cdb2d87a9f81e69e7","tid":2096474,"uid":8795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"爆料區咪有囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"今次又訓係邊個床下底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf54faef7ea8283f39c5068eb8bd8355b9aa99d","tid":2096474,"uid":8795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4fb0df76587a28f604556848f84ebd328937d510","tid":2096474,"uid":294121,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"e6cd9416a814b3df2b4f520cdb2d87a9f81e69e7","tid":2096474,"uid":8795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:30:12.000Z","msg":"爆料區咪有囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"今次又訓係邊個床下底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T07:44:08.000Z","msg":"你咪問下班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"